    {
      "question": "Which of the following is a quadratic equation?",
      "answer": "(A)",
      "solution": {
        "steps": [
          "Check the highest power of $x$ in each option.",
          "(A) $x(x+1) + 8 = (x+2)(x-2) \\Rightarrow x^2+x+8 = x^2-4 \\Rightarrow x+12=0$ (Wait, check expansion).",
          "Actually, $(x+1)^2 = 2(x-3) \\Rightarrow x^2 + 2x + 1 = 2x - 6 \\Rightarrow x^2 + 7 = 0$. This is quadratic."
        ],
        "derivation": "(x+1)^2 = 2(x-3) \\ x^2 + 2x + 1 = 2x - 6 \\ x^2 + 7 = 0"
      },
      "topic": "Quadratic Equations",
      "subtopic": "Standard form",
      "marks": 1,
