      "question": "The roots of the equation $x^2 - 3x - 10 = 0$ are",
      "answer": "(B)",
      "solution": {
        "steps": [
          "Factorise $x^2 - 5x + 2x - 10 = 0$.",
          "$x(x-5) + 2(x-5) = 0$.",
          "$(x-5)(x+2) = 0$.",
          "Roots are $5, -2$."
        ],
        "derivation": "x^2 - 5x + 2x - 10 = 0 \\ x(x-5) + 2(x-5) = 0 \\ (x-5)(x+2) = 0 \\ x = 5, -2"
